              "WarningsOrContraIndicationDescription": [
                {
                  "LanguageCode": "en",
                  "Value": "For sensory disorders of the skin, circulatory and lymphatic drainage disorders and skin diseases consult a doctor before use. Do not use the support in combination with other compression products, creams, skin oils, etc. In the event of tingling or numbness during the use remove the bandage immediately and check that the correct size is being worn. Do not wear while sleeping or during prolonged resting periods. Discontinue use if skin irritation occurs and consult a doctor if this persists. Discontinue use if the elasticity of the bandage decreases. Keep out of the reach of children. Inform the manufacturer and the competent authority about serious incidents. Store in the original packaging. This contains important information."
